{"tid":92374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國人無啦啦收到支那貨 肇因淘寶刷單惹的禍","createTime":"2017-01-23T14:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T08:21:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"309049b77bddc45c00c2af64070284846af876d0","tid":92374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"<strong>各國莫名收到淘寶爛貨 強國刷單客搞的鬼！</strong><br />\n2017-01-23  11:38<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英、美各地頻頻傳出有民眾<strong>無緣無故收到來自中國的包裹</strong>，包含仿冒的毛衣、運動鞋、太陽眼鏡等。<br />\n<br />\n一名住在英國的女子表示：「我打開包裹的時候，覺得很莫名其妙，我家裡沒有人穿得下那兩件衣服，它們又都是假貨。我當時根本沒買任何東西，所以覺得很怪。」<strong>原來，這不是因為她的銀行帳戶遭盜，而是中國刷單客為了網購賣家衝銷量及評價所致。</strong><br />\n<br />\n刷單客是假的買家，在各大網購通路偽造假的成交紀錄，一些公司或賣家僱用刷單客，讓自己的網路聲譽脫穎而出，吸引更多的顧客。<br />\n<br />\n由於中國網購平台禁止刷單行為，因此刷單客必須偽裝成真正的網購顧客，除了貨比三家以外，<span style=\"color: red;\">更為了讓購物紀錄更顯真實，留下不同的地址將商品寄往世界各地。</span><br />\n<br />\n一位經營刷單團體的代理人告訴《華爾街日報》：「他剛入刷單行列時，一個月約賺三到四千人民幣，但後來賺到一萬人民幣。」<br />\n<br />\n一名國外網友在社群網站上酸中國刷單客的行為：「他們就像約會不設標準、連醜八怪都可以上床的人，需要經驗讓自己看起來人模人樣，才能把到真正的辣妹。」<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1955906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1955906&d=DKV6guBTNI3Cds%2BtDyIkdAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d6c163c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1955906&h=d5a610ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1955906</a>"},{"pid":"2d33c4f9e1564ee37ec9949fc3935675fade32d2","tid":92374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6b144171045565d209638e4b00fdc649dc84f9","tid":92374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8c91d99d0dd92ab383151372f000c5fe633551","tid":92374,"uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"為左刷數據送埋d狗也不屌既垃圾比人，支那你係得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005ac1aebb8fdcd35c98f1b8f494b672f9085bd6","tid":92374,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"有d咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8acd3e4e48f71f03e42d4289bc330d1fe8d50b9","tid":92374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d044b648cfb46a1dfeefb419ec1c21e4ae557bf9","tid":92374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T21:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a23204ff2ccdf2fa098dc81f4620ab2ef707d6","tid":92374,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T22:52:08.000Z","msg":"但洗咩真係寄？"},{"pid":"d2cff33e7f9bc02b30fe96c147a5b89612d6e16d","tid":92374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}